    <section style="padding:0 1.5rem;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10H12V2z"/><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 10 10"/><path d="M12 12 4.35 6.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Zero mental load</h3>
          <p>LLM enrichment analyzes each incident and delivers probable cause with recommended steps — no more context switching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Easy to try</h3>
          <p>Docker Compose local setup gets the full stack running in minutes. Perfect for evaluation and development.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Open source</h3>
          <p>Apache 2.0 licensed. Deploy in your own AWS account with CDK — full control, no vendor lock-in.</p>
        </div>
