        <p style="color:#a3a3a3;font-size:0.95rem;margin:0;">One structured Slack message instead of a wall of alerts.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
        <img src="/assets/slack-mock.svg" alt="Junando incident notification in Slack" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:0.75rem;box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding:0 1.5rem;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin:0 0 0.5rem;">How It Works</h2>
      <p style="color:#a3a3a3;font-size:0.95rem;margin:0 0 2rem;">From alert to actionable notification in seconds</p>
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <img src="/assets/pipeline-diagram.svg" alt="Junando pipeline: Ingest, Deduplicate, Enrich, Notify" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:0.75rem;" />
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:0.75rem;text-align:left;">
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;">
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#3b82f6;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Step 1</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;font-weight:600;">Ingest</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#a3a3a3;line-height:1.5;">Alerts arrive via webhook (Alertmanager-compatible)</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;">
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#3b82f6;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Step 2</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;font-weight:600;">Deduplicate</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#a3a3a3;line-height:1.5;">Fingerprint-based clustering groups related alerts</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;">
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#3b82f6;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Step 3</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;font-weight:600;">Enrich</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#a3a3a3;line-height:1.5;">LLM analysis generates probable cause and recommendations</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;">
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#3b82f6;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Step 4</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;font-weight:600;">Notify</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#a3a3a3;line-height:1.5;">One structured message goes to Slack or Teams</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="trust-section" style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.75rem;">
          <div class="icon" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 22h20"/><path d="M15 10V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3l-4 9v11h18"/><path d="M7 11v7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin:0 0 0.5rem;">Built for real production stacks</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#a3a3a3;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
            Designed for teams running tens to hundreds of services. Plugs into your existing Alertmanager, Grafana, and AWS infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.75rem;">
          <div class="icon" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin:0 0 0.5rem;">Bring your own LLM</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#a3a3a3;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
            Configurable LLM providers — OpenRouter, Gemini, Claude, or your own endpoint. Keep control over cost, latency, and data residency.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

